│ 240          !Ty->isPPC_FP128Ty();                                                      │
│ 241 }                                                                                   │
│ 242                                                                                     │
│ 243 /// Returns the type of the given value/instruction \p V. If it is store,           │
│ 244 /// returns the type of its value operand, for Cmp - the types of the compare       │
